<CO>
   TCOMA TWRX FH CROP CCR CNNR CDIC
</CO>
<IN>
INITIAL STOCK OFFERINGS (INI)
STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
BOND MARKET NEWS (BON)
CDS, INTEREST RATES, COMMERCIAL PAPER (FIN)
</IN>
<GV>
TREASURY DEPARTMENT (TRE)
</GV>
<LP>
   The following U.S. Treasury, corporate and municipal
offerings are tentatively scheduled for sale this week,
according to Dow Jones Capital Markets Report:
                                                                                                       

                       U.S TREASURY
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>

                                                                                                       

   $18 billion in three- and six-month bills.
                                                                                                       

                         Wednesday
                                                                                                       

   $8 billion in seven-year notes.
                                                                                                       

                         CORPORATE
                                                                                                       

                       One Day This Week
                                                                                                       

   Cardinal Distribution Inc. -- $60 million of convertible
